OL,3,CLegal action taken over cancer
OL,4,Cscreening scandal
OL,6,FAlmost 30 women have taken legal
OL,7,Faction against Northern Ireland's five
OL,8,Fhealth trusts since 2013 over the
OL,9,Faccuracy of their cervical smears, UTV
OL,10,Fcan reveal.
OL,12,FThese litigations were launched even
OL,13,Fbefore the Southern Health Trust was
OL,14,Fforced to review 17,500 women's
OL,15,Fresults last year.
OL,17,FIt comes as campaigners prepare to
OL,18,Ftake their fight for a statutory
OL,19,Fpublic inquiry to Westminster.
