OL,6,FSandra and Ron Courtney spoke to UTV
OL,7,Fon Thursday as part of a special
OL,8,Finvestigation into the cervical cancer
OL,9,Fscreening scandal.
OL,11,FTheir daughter Lynsey, died after her
OL,12,Ffirst ever smear test was misread.
OL,14,FThey told UTV about their six-year
OL,15,Fbattle to get answers from the
OL,16,FSouthern Health Trust about what went
OL,17,Fwrong.
OL,19,F"We don't want to have to go through
OL,20,Fwhat we went through when it could be
OL,21,Fprevented.
