OL,6,F"You know, families shouldn't have to
OL,7,Fgo through that sort of trauma", they
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FSadly, Lynsey was not the only woman
OL,11,Ffailed by years of mistakes within the
OL,12,FSouthern Health Trusts screening lab.
OL,14,FErin Harbinson died last month
OL,15,Ffollowing three misread smears, and
OL,16,Fother women have had to be treated for
OL,17,Fcancer that was preventable.
