OL,6,FA major investigation by UTV revealed
OL,7,Fsignificant shortcomings stretching
OL,8,Fback as far as 2008 that were left
OL,9,Flargely unaddressed.
OL,11,FShortcomings that the Courtney family
OL,12,Ftried to draw attention to but nothing
OL,13,Fwas done.
OL,15,FUTV's findings have been met with
OL,16,Fanger by campaigners who want a
OL,17,Fstatutory public inquiry into the
OL,18,Fscandal.
