OL,6,F"We have spoken to the Health
OL,7,FMinister. We are really hoping that he
OL,8,Fwill, whenever he has all the data
OL,9,Fback and all the information from the
OL,10,FSouthern Trust at the end of the
OL,11,Freview, that he will consider
OL,12,Fdefinitely initiating a statutory
OL,13,Fpublic inquiry.
OL,15,FUTV can reveal that since 2013, 25
OL,16,Flegal actions have been launched
OL,17,Fagainst all five health trusts in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland in connection with
OL,19,Fmisread smear tests.
